# Finance Backend System

## 📌 Overview

This project is a backend system for managing financial records with role-based access control.

## 🚀 Features

* User management (Admin, Analyst, Viewer)
* Financial records CRUD
* Dashboard analytics (income, expense, balance)
* JWT Authentication
* Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)

## 🛠 Tech Stack

* Node.js
* Express.js
* MongoDB
* JWT

## 🔐 Roles

* Admin → Full access
* Analyst → Read + analytics
* Viewer → Read only

## 📊 APIs

### Auth

POST /auth/login

### Users

POST /users
GET /users

### Records

POST /records
GET /records
PUT /records/:id
DELETE /records/:id

### Dashboard

GET /dashboard/income
GET /dashboard/expense
GET /dashboard/balance

## ▶️ Run Project

```bash
npm install
node server.js
```

## 📌 Notes

* Authentication is done using JWT
* Role-based access enforced using middleware
